message.content: The kitchen has a modern design with a neutral color palette. There is a dark wooden cabinet with a handle on one side. A white countertop and wooden drawer fronts are installed beneath it. On the right side of the kitchen, there's a large window. Opposite to the cabinet, there's an oven under a cabinet door with a light above it. The countertop is clear except for two items: a box of cereal on the far left and a bag of groceries in the middle right. To the right of the counter, there's a white refrigerator with a wooden handle. Adjacent to the refrigerator, the oven is visible. A sink is installed under the window to the left of the cabinet. The floor has a tile pattern, and there are two boxes of cereal on it; one near the sink and another in front of the countertop. In front of the countertop, there's an image of a person with a speech bubble that reads "Happy Birthday". To the right of the kitchen, there's a dining area. The wall separating the kitchen from the dining area has light-colored tiles, and there is a lamp mounted on it above the cabinet.
